WEBVTT

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary Diaries</b></font>

00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:19.450
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}The Apothecary <font color="#000000">Diaries</font></b></font>

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:33.980
<font size="10">{\an1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on
 are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.</font>

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:49.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Take a look, Maomao!</font>

00:01:49.540 --> 00:01:51.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wow, this is impressive.</font>

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:53.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I know, right?</font>

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:56.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I see, this is why they bothered to summon me.</i></font>

00:01:56.670 --> 00:01:58.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}It's a great mirror, isn't it?</font>

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:01.680
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 28: Mirrors</font>

00:01:58.940 --> 00:02:01.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Can you tell what it's made of?</font>

00:02:02.230 --> 00:02:05.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This reflection... Is it glass?</font>

00:02:06.290 --> 00:02:07.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Correct.</font>

00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:10.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Honestly, it's like there are 
two Lady Gyokuyous.</font>

00:02:10.700 --> 00:02:13.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Making mirrors out of glass is difficult.</i></font>

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:15.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The only way to get them 
is through trade with the west.</i></font>

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:17.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Meaning this is extremely expensive.</i></font>

00:02:18.250 --> 00:02:22.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>If I broke this by accident, they'd have
every right to chop my head off.</i></font>

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:26.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We had a glass hand mirror before, 
but Yinghua broke it.</font>

00:02:26.510 --> 00:02:28.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Please don't remind me about that!</font>

00:02:28.950 --> 00:02:31.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'm glad Lady Gyokuyou is an even-tempered person...</i></font>

00:02:35.390 --> 00:02:37.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Does this interest you, Maomao?</font>

00:02:37.320 --> 00:02:40.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. I wonder how it works?</font>

00:02:41.130 --> 00:02:44.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If we could mass-produce this domestically, 
we could make a lot of money...</font>

00:02:44.940 --> 00:02:46.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, right.</font>

00:02:47.160 --> 00:02:51.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This mirror is a gift from 
the foreign special envoy.</font>

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:52.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A special envoy?</font>

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The quack doctor mentioned something like that.</i></font>

00:02:56.430 --> 00:03:01.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The large-scale caravan was an advance 
party to the special envoy, or something.</i></font>

00:03:01.990 --> 00:03:05.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think they gave one to all of 
the high-ranking concubines, though.</font>

00:03:05.390 --> 00:03:07.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't phrase it like that.</font>

00:03:08.440 --> 00:03:11.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There's four high-ranking concubines, 
including Concubine Gyokuyou.</i></font>

00:03:11.420 --> 00:03:14.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A special envoy would 
have to treat them fairly.</i></font>

00:03:15.590 --> 00:03:19.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Bringing four giant mirrors like this 
must have been hard,</i></font>

00:03:19.020 --> 00:03:22.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>whether it was over the desert or by sea.</i></font>

00:03:23.610 --> 00:03:26.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>For them to go through 
all of that for the concubines,</i></font>

00:03:26.140 --> 00:03:30.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>they might be trying to start 
a big business deal with our nation.</i></font>

00:03:31.350 --> 00:03:33.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Xiaomao, may I have a moment?</font>

00:03:34.270 --> 00:03:36.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Gaoshun, what is it?</font>

00:03:37.530 --> 00:03:41.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's something I would
 like your opinion on.</font>

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:43.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Lady Hongniang, may I borrow this room?</font>

00:03:43.930 --> 00:03:47.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, that's fine, but is it a difficult topic?</font>

00:03:51.940 --> 00:03:55.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Lady Hongniang joined us, 
saying I shouldn't be alone with him,</i></font>

00:03:55.840 --> 00:04:00.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but she lost all interest once she 
found out Gaoshun has a wife and child.</i></font>

00:04:01.570 --> 00:04:05.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, I don't know if I can be of any help, 
but what did you have in mind?</font>

00:04:06.370 --> 00:04:09.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, an acquaintance of mine 
is very concerned.</font>

00:04:10.190 --> 00:04:12.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's a very strange situation, but...</font>

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:16.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A rich family has two daughters.</font>

00:04:16.780 --> 00:04:19.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They're close in age and
 have similar appearances.</font>

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:23.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The girls were loved deeply by their 
parents, but when they came of age,</font>

00:04:23.070 --> 00:04:24.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">their parents became
 overprotective of them.</font>

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:30.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They were never allowed to leave
 the house, not even together.</font>

00:04:30.360 --> 00:04:32.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A lady-in-waiting was assigned 
to monitor them,</font>

00:04:32.450 --> 00:04:35.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and they spent their days in their house.</font>

00:04:36.030 --> 00:04:39.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The lady-in-waiting felt sorry for them 
and took them out occasionally,</font>

00:04:40.020 --> 00:04:42.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but the father found out.</font>

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:45.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He stationed male servants
 outside the room to watch them,</font>

00:04:46.180 --> 00:04:49.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and locked the doors at night 
so that they couldn't get out.</font>

00:04:51.150 --> 00:04:56.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The daughters were introverts, so they 
spent all day on their embroidery,</font>

00:04:56.550 --> 00:04:57.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but one day...</font>

00:04:58.220 --> 00:04:59.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Father, my little sister...</font>

00:05:00.570 --> 00:05:02.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She is pregnant, carrying the child of a wizard!</font>

00:05:06.760 --> 00:05:08.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's...</font>

00:05:08.060 --> 00:05:10.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A strange story.</font>

00:05:10.220 --> 00:05:13.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Didn't the lady-in-waiting 
just sneak them out again?</font>

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:17.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, the lady-in-waiting had already
 been fired as a warning to the others.</font>

00:05:18.670 --> 00:05:21.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The new lady-in-waiting didn't 
interact much with the daughters.</font>

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:28.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well... in that case, though it would be 
improper, what about the servant men?</font>

00:05:28.740 --> 00:05:30.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That would be difficult as well.</font>

00:05:30.910 --> 00:05:35.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They weren't allowed to approach
 the room, even while monitoring them.</font>

00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:40.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That is quite a conundrum, but it seems
 outside my realm of knowledge.</font>

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:45.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">For example, if the ask was, "Is it possible 
to become pregnant without seeing a man?"</font>

00:05:45.340 --> 00:05:46.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I could explain it.</font>

00:05:46.920 --> 00:05:48.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Does that ever happen?</font>

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:51.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The body can trick itself 
into believing it's pregnant</font>

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:54.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">without actually becoming so.</font>

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:58.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There was a case in the brothel 
where a young courtesan</font>

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:01.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">claimed that she was carrying 
the child of the man she loves.</font>

00:06:01.420 --> 00:06:04.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Without actually becoming pregnant?</font>

00:06:04.210 --> 00:06:09.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Exactly. She began missing her periods, 
and her breasts and stomach grew tender.</font>

00:06:09.330 --> 00:06:12.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A strongly held belief can have 
a powerful effect on the body.</font>

00:06:13.830 --> 00:06:16.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are you sure the younger 
daughter was pregnant?</font>

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, yes...</font>

00:06:19.410 --> 00:06:21.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's just say she was.</font>

00:06:22.940 --> 00:06:28.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The problem is, how was she able 
to sneak out past the surveillance?</font>

00:06:28.260 --> 00:06:32.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, do you know how they were being watched?</font>

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:35.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. Here is a diagram.</font>

00:06:37.540 --> 00:06:40.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The sisters lived in a separate 
building on the north side,</font>

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:44.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">connected to the main house 
by a corridor on the west.</font>

00:06:44.380 --> 00:06:45.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where is the washroom?</font>

00:06:45.950 --> 00:06:47.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Inside the separate building.</font>

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:50.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If the younger daughter were to escape...</font>

00:06:50.940 --> 00:06:53.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The only way in or out 
is the corridor on the west side.</font>

00:06:53.950 --> 00:06:58.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There are windows on the east and south sides, 
but the servant men were watching those.</font>

00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:02.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Where were the servants 
watching the windows from?</font>

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The south window was watched from
 the third floor of the main house,</font>

00:07:06.440 --> 00:07:09.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">while the east window was
 being watched from the first floor.</font>

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:14.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm. They seem to have 
a very limited field of vision.</font>

00:07:14.210 --> 00:07:16.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could they see inside the room at all?</font>

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:22.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not really, but the daughters were often 
doing needlework by the window.</font>

00:07:22.370 --> 00:07:25.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A strange hobby, embroidery.</font>

00:07:25.740 --> 00:07:28.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They came from a pastoral culture.</font>

00:07:28.940 --> 00:07:33.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hmm... It sounds like 
he's hiding something important.</i></font>

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:38.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The windows on the south and west 
seem to be in the same room.</i></font>

00:07:38.990 --> 00:07:42.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The daughters have separate
 bedrooms for themselves.</i></font>

00:07:42.620 --> 00:07:45.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Was this separate building 
originally for guests?</font>

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:47.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm impressed that you noticed that.</font>

00:07:47.420 --> 00:07:49.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How many men were watching?</font>

00:07:49.420 --> 00:07:52.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Two. They were always 
stationed in the same spot.</font>

00:07:54.690 --> 00:07:57.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He knows the details quite well.</i></font>

00:07:57.070 --> 00:08:01.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Yet, it feels like he's 
not telling me everything...</i></font>

00:08:01.230 --> 00:08:04.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is he really talking about 
an "acquaintance" of his?</i></font>

00:08:04.940 --> 00:08:08.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Hmm... I don't know 
if I want to bring this up...</i></font>

00:08:10.010 --> 00:08:11.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">By the way, Xiaomao.</font>

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:14.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi sent a message.</font>

00:08:14.030 --> 00:08:17.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He wanted to apologize for the delay 
in delivering the ox bezoar.</font>

00:08:17.010 --> 00:08:17.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm?</font>

00:08:18.510 --> 00:08:19.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The bezoar!</i></font>

00:08:19.460 --> 00:08:21.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>That's true, he hasn't handed it over yet.</i></font>

00:08:21.780 --> 00:08:25.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I didn't want another headbutt, so I kept
 my mouth shut, but he is indeed late.</i></font>

00:08:26.030 --> 00:08:29.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sorry. It seems like demand 
for it suddenly went up.</font>

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:32.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why so suddenly?</font>

00:08:34.490 --> 00:08:36.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've heard recently that Master Jinshi</font>

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:40.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">has been gifted many rare
 medicines from all sorts of people.</font>

00:08:40.420 --> 00:08:43.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rumor has it that he's quite
 passionately searching for them.</font>

00:08:43.580 --> 00:08:47.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">W-Well, anyway, please take this.</font>

00:08:59.650 --> 00:09:01.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What is this?</font>

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:03.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It is a bear gall.</font>

00:09:03.150 --> 00:09:04.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's a bear's gallbladder, dried.</font>

00:09:04.820 --> 00:09:07.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's bitter, but it's valued for its use</font>

00:09:07.300 --> 00:09:08.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">in medicines for the digestive system!</font>

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:11.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm glad you like it.</font>

00:09:11.310 --> 00:09:14.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think Master Jinshi wanted to 
deliver it to you personally.</font>

00:09:17.100 --> 00:09:20.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, did you notice anything?</font>

00:09:21.490 --> 00:09:24.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. Can you wait for a moment?</font>

00:09:32.270 --> 00:09:34.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's say that these nuts 
are the two daughters.</font>

00:09:35.070 --> 00:09:38.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Are these the spots that they always sit in?</font>

00:09:38.510 --> 00:09:39.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:09:40.010 --> 00:09:44.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Two people watching them, 
always from the same spot every day.</font>

00:09:44.700 --> 00:09:45.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What if...</font>

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:48.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I put a mirror here, like this.</font>

00:09:50.600 --> 00:09:53.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It does look like another nut is there.</font>

00:09:53.370 --> 00:09:58.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What if there was a large mirror here, 
near the east window?</font>

00:09:59.230 --> 00:10:01.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It would be a good distance away 
from the watcher,</font>

00:10:01.570 --> 00:10:04.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">so it would be hard to tell, 
even if it looked a bit unnatural.</font>

00:10:04.490 --> 00:10:07.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, you're saying there was 
only one daughter in the room,</font>

00:10:07.050 --> 00:10:10.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and the other was an image in the mirror?</font>

00:10:11.880 --> 00:10:13.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If the daughters looked similar,</font>

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:16.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">it may have been difficult 
for the watchers to tell them apart.</font>

00:10:16.850 --> 00:10:19.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But Maomao, what about the needlework?</font>

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:23.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They were working on
 different things, were they not?</font>

00:10:23.050 --> 00:10:28.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I heard they were stitching 
animals, such as birds or rabbits.</font>

00:10:28.220 --> 00:10:29.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, as an example...</font>

00:10:30.080 --> 00:10:32.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Take an image like this.</font>

00:10:34.860 --> 00:10:39.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When I flip this picture upside down, 
doesn't the smile now look like a frown?</font>

00:10:41.110 --> 00:10:44.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So you're saying the embroidery 
was part of the trick, too?</font>

00:10:45.010 --> 00:10:47.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maybe they were working on embroidery</font>

00:10:47.900 --> 00:10:52.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">that looked like a different image 
when seen through a mirror.</font>

00:10:52.330 --> 00:10:55.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If so, one could be actually doing 
needlework by the southern window,</font>

00:10:55.550 --> 00:11:00.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">while the other escapes 
out of the exit on the west.</font>

00:11:00.420 --> 00:11:01.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:11:01.550 --> 00:11:06.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I guess using that method, it would be 
possible to sneak out and meet someone.</font>

00:11:06.810 --> 00:11:11.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The large mirror that the foreign 
envoys brought was so beautiful.</i></font>

00:11:11.860 --> 00:11:14.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>From a distance, it would be hard 
to tell a reflection from reality.</i></font>

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:19.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A long time ago, when my dad 
went to study abroad in the west,</i></font>

00:11:19.070 --> 00:11:22.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>he told me that needlework was common 
among high-class daughters.</i></font>

00:11:23.490 --> 00:11:28.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Master Gaoshun said a girl from a rich family 
snuck out of the house to get pregnant,</i></font>

00:11:29.210 --> 00:11:32.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but I don't know how accurate that story is.</i></font>

00:11:32.540 --> 00:11:36.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Maybe she was carrying 
a bigger secret instead of a child.</i></font>

00:11:37.750 --> 00:11:39.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I suppose sometimes, one would need to</i></font>

00:11:39.570 --> 00:11:42.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>accept someone who is 
suspected of being a spy as a guest.</i></font>

00:11:42.810 --> 00:11:46.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But I'm not going to question that 
and get myself too involved.</i></font>

00:11:46.770 --> 00:11:48.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>More importantly...</i></font>

00:11:51.160 --> 00:11:54.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What should I make with this bear gall?!</font>

00:11:58.940 --> 00:12:02.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">An otherworldly beauty 
that sheds pearls as tears?</font>

00:12:03.090 --> 00:12:06.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yeah, the high-ranking official in charge of 
the welcoming party came begging for help.</font>

00:12:07.330 --> 00:12:10.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Master Jinshi, you don't have 
to accept any more work...</font>

00:12:11.100 --> 00:12:12.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I know.</font>

00:12:15.020 --> 00:12:19.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's not just the mirrors. 
What are the envoys thinking?</font>

00:12:21.890 --> 00:12:24.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Apothecary, have you ever heard a story</font>

00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:27.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">of an otherworldly beauty 
who sheds pearls as tears?</font>

00:12:29.220 --> 00:12:30.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh? What is it?</font>

00:12:30.940 --> 00:12:32.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>I'd love to say,</i></font>

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:35.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>"There's an otherworldly beauty 
in front of me right here..."</i></font>

00:12:37.020 --> 00:12:39.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What do you mean by "pearls as tears"?</font>

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:42.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't know the details, but...</font>

00:12:43.270 --> 00:12:45.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She was a beautiful woman, like a moon fairy.</font>

00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:49.620
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When she danced, lights danced
 with her as if blessing her.</font>

00:12:49.980 --> 00:12:53.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When she cried, the tears turned 
into pearls as they fell down.</font>

00:12:54.290 --> 00:12:57.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think she was a courtesan 
from the pleasure district, but...</font>

00:12:57.630 --> 00:13:01.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A moon fairy? Where did this come from?</font>

00:13:01.060 --> 00:13:03.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's a serious request from 
the special envoy with us now.</font>

00:13:04.280 --> 00:13:06.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The special envoy? From the west?</font>

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:10.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. When they were young, 
the envoy's grandfather told</font>

00:13:10.740 --> 00:13:13.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">the story of the moon fairy, 
over and over again.</font>

00:13:14.640 --> 00:13:18.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, now they're asking me to find her, 
so that they can meet her.</font>

00:13:18.970 --> 00:13:22.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Their grandfather? That must mean 
this is a pretty old story.</font>

00:13:22.800 --> 00:13:27.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. It's difficult, but they're 
important diplomatic partners.</font>

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:28.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'd like to respond to the best of my ability.</font>

00:13:29.590 --> 00:13:32.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Does this remind you of anything, even a rumor?</font>

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:35.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Fifty years ago...</i></font>

00:13:35.660 --> 00:13:38.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>A dancer from the pleasure 
district... Moon fairy...</i></font>

00:13:39.230 --> 00:13:39.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh!</font>

00:13:40.170 --> 00:13:44.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is obviously decades ago, 
so who knows if she's still alive...</font>

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:46.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's very much alive.</font>

00:13:46.650 --> 00:13:47.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Really?!</font>

00:13:48.210 --> 00:13:53.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Really, and in fact, you've met her 
before in the pleasure district.</font>

00:13:53.400 --> 00:13:54.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I have?</font>

00:13:54.680 --> 00:13:55.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes.</font>

00:13:55.570 --> 00:13:58.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I don't remember meeting anyone 
matching the description...</font>

00:13:58.900 --> 00:14:02.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's no surprise that you 
can't think of her immediately.</font>

00:14:02.900 --> 00:14:04.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could it be?</font>

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:09.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Indeed, it's the old lady 
of the Verdigris House.</font>

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:13.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh, what is she like?</font>

00:14:15.640 --> 00:14:20.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She'll come any time, as long as 
you can pay. What do you think?</font>

00:14:20.340 --> 00:14:22.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">W-Well, that's...</font>

00:14:23.040 --> 00:14:27.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The envoy knows the person is 
from fifty years ago.</font>

00:14:27.920 --> 00:14:30.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Couldn't you just find 
a different beautiful woman?</font>

00:14:30.090 --> 00:14:35.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, we already hosted a welcoming 
party with beautiful women.</font>

00:14:35.800 --> 00:14:37.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They might not have been moon fairies,</font>

00:14:37.760 --> 00:14:40.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but I still think we brought in 
some top-level beauties.</font>

00:14:44.810 --> 00:14:49.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They didn't seem to be satisfied. 
In fact, they seemed to laugh it off.</font>

00:14:50.060 --> 00:14:52.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Who is this guy?</i></font>

00:14:52.100 --> 00:14:55.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm sorry, but did any of these top-level 
beauties provide any overnight services—</font>

00:14:55.860 --> 00:14:57.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maomao!</font>

00:14:57.250 --> 00:14:59.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No, we couldn't do that.</font>

00:15:00.270 --> 00:15:02.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The envoy is female.</font>

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:06.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Ah, so that's why they came 
to Master Jinshi for help.</i></font>

00:15:07.230 --> 00:15:11.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He has beauty that would impress 
anyone, and is technically male.</i></font>

00:15:11.850 --> 00:15:15.550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He does have what it takes 
to make a woman go head over heels.</i></font>

00:15:16.210 --> 00:15:18.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But he could cause trouble, too.</i></font>

00:15:19.310 --> 00:15:22.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What if she took his seduction seriously 
and demanded he stay overnight?</i></font>

00:15:22.440 --> 00:15:23.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He can't deliver.</i></font>

00:15:24.360 --> 00:15:28.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Of course, being a special envoy 
as a woman must have taught her</i></font>

00:15:28.500 --> 00:15:31.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>to refrain from such careless acts,</i></font>

00:15:31.310 --> 00:15:33.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>but it's a risk worth avoiding.</i></font>

00:15:34.420 --> 00:15:38.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How important is this envoy?</font>

00:15:38.650 --> 00:15:42.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Let's just say they completely control 
the western and northern trade points.</font>

00:15:43.120 --> 00:15:45.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The latest caravan was so large</font>

00:15:45.700 --> 00:15:48.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">because both nations want to 
advance talks of new trades.</font>

00:15:49.470 --> 00:15:50.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see.</font>

00:15:50.970 --> 00:15:54.140
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I hear in distant lands, marriages 
take place across international lines,</font>

00:15:54.140 --> 00:15:57.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">causing beautiful men and women 
to become quite commonplace.</font>

00:15:58.100 --> 00:16:01.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>For someone from such a nation 
to call someone a moon fairy...</i></font>

00:16:02.640 --> 00:16:05.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Did she put hallucinogens 
in the incense or something?</font>

00:16:05.570 --> 00:16:07.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Do people do that?</font>

00:16:07.520 --> 00:16:09.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Not usually, but it would be the quickest way.</font>

00:16:10.290 --> 00:16:12.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That would cause a diplomatic disaster.</font>

00:16:13.850 --> 00:16:17.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm grasping at straws here. 
Is there any information from back then?</font>

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:20.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>He really is distraught.</i></font>

00:16:20.850 --> 00:16:23.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Well, let's bring in the straw to grasp.</i></font>

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:27.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thanks for coming all the way out here.</font>

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:32.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is a strange ask.</font>

00:16:33.820 --> 00:16:37.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What a boring place. Not even a cup of tea?</font>

00:16:38.290 --> 00:16:40.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This is just a visitation room, of sorts.</font>

00:16:41.640 --> 00:16:46.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Old lady, did you welcome 
a foreign envoy in the past?</font>

00:16:46.150 --> 00:16:50.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes, I did. It must have been 
over 50 years ago.</font>

00:16:50.510 --> 00:16:53.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This was back in the age of the emperor 
before the previous one.</font>

00:16:53.780 --> 00:16:56.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The city was originally a town 
built on an ancient ruin,</font>

00:16:56.980 --> 00:16:59.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and we had a bunch of tourists visiting.</font>

00:17:00.290 --> 00:17:04.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">When they suddenly decided to make 
this popular spot the capital,</font>

00:17:04.610 --> 00:17:07.120
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">there was a bit of turmoil.</font>

00:17:07.630 --> 00:17:10.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Anyway, the capital was still new, 
so we didn't have a great castle</font>

00:17:10.440 --> 00:17:13.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and nowhere to welcome guests.</font>

00:17:13.050 --> 00:17:18.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The higher-ups couldn't think of anything, 
so they used a remaining ruin.</font>

00:17:18.890 --> 00:17:20.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It used to be some kind of ceremonial site.</font>

00:17:20.730 --> 00:17:24.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It had a pretty pond and 
buildings next to an orchard.</font>

00:17:24.980 --> 00:17:26.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is that...</i></font>

00:17:26.990 --> 00:17:29.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>There was a ruined orchard 
on the north side of the rear palace</i></font>

00:17:29.540 --> 00:17:31.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>that I visited the other day.</i></font>

00:17:31.810 --> 00:17:36.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It's not out of the question that the party
 venue might now be part of the rear palace.</i></font>

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:42.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was selected as the main dancer in 
the performance using that ruin as a stage.</font>

00:17:43.120 --> 00:17:44.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why you?</font>

00:17:44.580 --> 00:17:46.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well, I was the highest-class courtesan</font>

00:17:46.380 --> 00:17:48.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">in the whole pleasure district back then.</font>

00:17:48.960 --> 00:17:51.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was the main dancer, and about 
a dozen others danced with me.</font>

00:17:52.380 --> 00:17:56.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She looks like a dead twig now, but...</i></font>

00:17:56.200 --> 00:17:59.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That said, I think the biggest 
reason was my build.</font>

00:18:01.260 --> 00:18:05.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I was very tall, and had a very curvy body.</font>

00:18:05.690 --> 00:18:10.640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It does make sense to assign someone 
with a bigger body as the main dancer.</i></font>

00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:11.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That said...</font>

00:18:12.020 --> 00:18:15.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A lot of the event was improvised, 
so we had difficulty preparing.</font>

00:18:16.650 --> 00:18:19.160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We had to plan everything, 
like the phases of the moon,</font>

00:18:19.160 --> 00:18:23.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">and removed obstacles 
to give the guests a better view.</font>

00:18:24.270 --> 00:18:27.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The nearby orchard meant lots of insects,</font>

00:18:27.220 --> 00:18:31.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">so we went in and picked out 
every single larva from the leaves.</font>

00:18:31.730 --> 00:18:36.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We did end up getting insects 
around the torches, though.</font>

00:18:36.780 --> 00:18:42.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Even after all that work, there were idiots 
who tampered with my costume that night.</font>

00:18:42.940 --> 00:18:45.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They rubbed insect carcasses on it.</font>

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:49.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But I was too tough for them.</font>

00:18:49.230 --> 00:18:52.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I used my outfit skillfully to hide it.</font>

00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:57.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The audience ate it up, 
and the idiots seemed so angry.</font>

00:18:57.020 --> 00:19:00.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've heard that story so many times. 
Got anything else?</font>

00:19:00.780 --> 00:19:02.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Have some respect!</font>

00:19:10.130 --> 00:19:13.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>What a beautiful picture. 
I haven't seen this before.</i></font>

00:19:13.570 --> 00:19:16.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>It must be precious to the old granny as well.</i></font>

00:19:17.310 --> 00:19:22.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Who would've known this mesmerizing 
beauty would become a penny-pincher...</i></font>

00:19:24.660 --> 00:19:30.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This painting was commissioned by 
the envoy after he returned home.</font>

00:19:30.410 --> 00:19:32.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Saying he saw a "moon goddess" or something.</font>

00:19:32.850 --> 00:19:36.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Ah, I see. This picture is beautified as well.</font>

00:19:36.360 --> 00:19:38.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What did you say?</font>

00:19:38.020 --> 00:19:39.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Nothing.</font>

00:19:40.250 --> 00:19:43.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So, the envoy never set foot in our land again,</font>

00:19:44.580 --> 00:19:47.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but he sent this to me through the caravan.</font>

00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:52.560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But granny, you were just 
doing your job as usual, right?</font>

00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:54.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why did he like you so much?</font>

00:19:54.330 --> 00:19:57.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How should I know?</font>

00:20:00.170 --> 00:20:03.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>The old lady can see things objectively.</i></font>

00:20:03.970 --> 00:20:05.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>She probably isn't exaggerating.</i></font>

00:20:06.090 --> 00:20:07.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>But...</i></font>

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:10.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Even if the old lady was beautiful back then,</i></font>

00:20:11.500 --> 00:20:14.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>what caused them to call her a goddess?</i></font>

00:20:17.320 --> 00:20:19.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hmm, I don't know.</font>

00:20:19.970 --> 00:20:23.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Should we find someone who 
looks like the person in the picture?</font>

00:20:23.830 --> 00:20:26.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's all I can think of.</font>

00:20:26.660 --> 00:20:31.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Honestly, finding a tall woman 
who looks like this would be difficult.</i></font>

00:20:32.200 --> 00:20:36.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why don't we just look for a tall woman, 
not necessarily one that looks like this?</font>

00:20:37.140 --> 00:20:42.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's shrunk quite a bit now, but she said
 she was 175 centimeters tall back then.</font>

00:20:42.760 --> 00:20:44.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That is quite tall.</font>

00:20:44.930 --> 00:20:50.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. She was a skilled dancer, and her long 
limbs helped make her dances look even better.</font>

00:20:50.730 --> 00:20:56.180
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But finding a tall woman on par 
with her beauty would be difficult.</font>

00:20:56.180 --> 00:20:59.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The envoys are about that tall.</font>

00:20:59.250 --> 00:21:02.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If we find someone too small, 
they might appear like children.</font>

00:21:03.700 --> 00:21:07.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The "envoys"? There are more than one?</font>

00:21:08.150 --> 00:21:11.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. They are cousins 
with the same grandfather.</font>

00:21:12.380 --> 00:21:16.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>From the way they described it, 
the envoys must be quite pretty as well.</i></font>

00:21:17.270 --> 00:21:21.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>So we have to find someone 
who's more than 175 centimeters tall,</i></font>

00:21:21.290 --> 00:21:25.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>whose beauty would impress another beauty...</i></font>

00:21:26.330 --> 00:21:26.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh.</font>

00:21:28.380 --> 00:21:31.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I found someone. A very suitable candidate.</font>

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:35.480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A beautiful person taller 
than 175 centimeters, right?</font>

00:21:35.480 --> 00:21:36.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh!</font>

00:21:40.290 --> 00:21:40.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Huh?</font>

00:21:42.060 --> 00:21:43.780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you trying to say?</font>

00:22:05.640 --> 00:22:07.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wow!</font>

00:23:44.980 --> 00:23:59.910
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22">{\an7}Next Time</font>

00:23:56.450 --> 00:23:59.910
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20">{\an3}Episode 29: Moon Fairy</font>

00:23:56.580 --> 00:23:58.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>{\an8}Next time: "Moon Fairy."</i></font>

